Download ANT 
Go To SF --> Go To tools --> Download Force.com migration tool
Go to Salesforce_ant and copy ant-Salesforce.jar
Paste it in --> Apache ANT to the lib folder 

Above is done to make an intraction between SF and ant 

Now 
Set the environmental variables 
Go To My Computer and left click to Properties
Advance System Variables 
Environmental Variables

Need to set
AND_Home 
Java_Home
Path

Go to Salesforce Ant, ther will be 2 files 
build.properties --> Will save the username and Password 
build.xml
